@startuml
title ERC-20 Transfer Fetch - Sequence Diagram
actor User
participant CLI
participant Fetcher
participant RPC
participant PostgreSQL

User -> CLI: run fetch command
CLI -> CLI: Parse parameters
CLI -> Fetcher: fetch_logs(network, start, end)
Fetcher -> RPC: eth_getLogs request
RPC --> Fetcher: logs response
Fetcher -> CLI: decoded & normalized logs
CLI -> PostgreSQL: insert batch (conflict-safe)
CLI -> PostgreSQL: update fetch_progress
CLI --> User: fetch complete
@enduml